OL,3,CPolice search for missing soldier
OL,5,FPolice in North Yorkshire are
OL,6,Fsearching for a missing soldier who
OL,7,Ffailed to return to his barracks at
OL,8,FCatterick Garrison after a night out
OL,9,Fin Selby.
OL,11,FTwenty-eight-year-old Ryan Rudd was
OL,12,Flast seen at the New Inn in Selby in
OL,13,Fthe early hours of Sunday 15 February
OL,14,Fafter going on a night out with two
OL,15,Ffriends on Valentine's Day.
OL,17,FHe failed to return home or to his
OL,18,Fbase at Catterick Garrison and since
OL,19,Fthen has been out of contact with
OL,20,Ffamily, friends and colleagues.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/2
