OL,3,CPolice search for missing soldier
OL,5,FNorth Yorkshire Police said: "We are
OL,6,Fappealing to anyone who may have seen
OL,7,Fhim in Selby on 14/15 February or has
OL,8,Fseen him since then, to contact us as
OL,9,Fa matter of urgency."
OL,11,FRyan is described as white, around 5ft
OL,12,F8in tall, of slim build with dark
OL,13,Fbrown hair and was last seen he was
OL,14,Fwearing a black t-shirt, blue hooded
OL,15,Ftop and black trousers.
OL,17,FA CCTV image has been released from
OL,18,Fthe pub in Selby on the night he went
OL,19,Fmissing.
